trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected"></xref> events of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 処理するメソッドを表す、 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected"> </xref>と<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected"></xref>のイベント、 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref>コントロール。

trans-unit.source: The WebPartConnectionsEventHandler class defines a handler delegate for two events that occur on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control: the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: WebPartConnectionsEventHandler クラス上で発生する&2; つのイベント ハンドラー デリゲートの定義、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>コントロール:<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>イベントおよび<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>イベント</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>。

trans-unit.source: The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnected%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 処理するメソッド、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>イベントは、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnected%2A>メソッド</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnected%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>。

trans-unit.source: The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnected%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 処理するメソッド、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>イベントは、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnected%2A>メソッド</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnected%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>。

trans-unit.source: In both cases, the event data are contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: どちらの場合、イベント データが含まれている、<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs>オブジェクト</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs>。
